        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer115347240" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2111680207102212189">This is not a silver fork novel, more of an adventure in the Geoffrey Farnol tradition, based on real events. I don&apos;t think Heyer had the skills to pull it off: her research of facts is impeccable, but she doesn&apos;t understand the paradigm, so her characters read as cardboard cutouts.</span>
  <span id="freeText2111680207102212189" style="display:none">This is not a silver fork novel, more of an adventure in the Geoffrey Farnol tradition, based on real events. I don't think Heyer had the skills to pull it off: her research of facts is impeccable, but she doesn't understand the paradigm, so her characters read as cardboard cutouts.</span>
